            <title>[HBASE-9357] Rest server shouldn&apos;t need to initiate ZK connection to print usage information</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-9357</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When there&apos;s no ZK available, running `bin/hbase rest` must timeout before printing usage information. Initiating a connection should happen after parsing CLI options, not before.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
